VMTK in 3D Slicer 4
-------------------

Until extensions are available in Slicer4, copy this module to Slicer4/QTModules/ and include it for compilation.

The VMTK libraries get fetched through a Superbuild External mechanism.

After installation, the VMTK classes can be accessed in Slicer4 Python like this example:

>> from libvtkvmtkSegmentationPython import *
>> fastMarching = vtkvmtkFastMarchingUpwindGradientImageFilter()
>> fastMarching.SetInput(..)
>> ...
